{# Admin_Console 403 Forbidden page (task 39.1).
   Validates: Requirements 11.6 (RBAC denial → HTTP 403 + AccessDenied audit)
   Design   : §14.3 (Denial), §6 Admin

   Rendered by `requirePolicy(...)` (src/modules/security/policies.ts) when
   an authenticated internal user (Super_Admin / HR / Department_Head) hits
   a route whose §14.1 policy does not grant their role. The guard has
   already recorded an `access_denied` audit event before this renders.

   Standalone document (no shared admin layout exists yet) — mirrors the
   header pattern of `admin/jobs/kanban.njk`.

   Inputs:
     - role     : the session role that was denied (string)
     - policy   : the policy name that gated the route (string)
     - cspNonce : nonce passed through from the route (may be undefined)
#}
<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>403 · Akses Ditolak</title>
    {% if cspNonce %}<meta name="csp-nonce" content="{{ cspNonce }}">{% endif %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/app.css">
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">
    <header class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/admin/jobs" class="font-semibold">PT Buana Megah · Admin</a>
        <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">{{ role }}</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-6xl font-bold text-slate-300">403</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Akses ditolak</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">
        Peran <span class="font-mono font-medium">{{ role }}</span> tidak
        memiliki izin untuk tindakan ini.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">
        You don't have permission to perform this action.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="/admin/jobs"
          class="inline-block rounded bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 text-white hover:bg-slate-700"
        >← Kembali ke daftar lowongan</a>
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
